          <p>Father-daughter duo Owen and Emily Bannister joined forces to start Owen Bannister Ltd.</p>
          <br>
          <p>Owen is 62 and had considered retirement, having worked for more than 20 years in IT consultancy and management around the globe.</p>
          <br>
