          <br>
          <p>Bringing together their skills and experience in design and IT they formed Owen Bannister Ltd in 2013.</p>
          <br>
          <p>The company designs and builds simple, affordable, Software as a Service (SaaS) solutions specifically for small businesses and sole traders. As small business owners themselves they understand the specific needs and problems that small businesses face.</p>
          <br>
